04:41.698 --> 04:53.710
involved in it during your long 40-odd year span? 
That is an exceedingly difficult question

04:55.968 --> 05:05.579
to answer. And

05:05.599 --> 05:22.819
I wouldn't look at a single development as much as a 
in some ways, a unification of the field.

05:31.718 --> 05:38.708
