book on the oceans. And I think that

05:41.051 --> 05:51.625
these sub-disciplines, although they 
contribute really to the understanding The final

05:52.600 --> 06:01.888
use that we make of those is going to require the 
cooperation of people of different disciplines.

06:03.129 --> 06:06.212
This is still hard to get across in this present 
day. But I think it doesn't mean that people have to

06:06.773 --> 06:14.860
be experts in all the different areas, because no 
one can. But at least there should be free

06:15.681 --> 06:22.607
communication from one group to another. There's 
far too much effort that has been spent on pursuing

06:23.043 --> 06:36.698
things that, from another viewpoint, would have 
been perfectly illogical.

06:39.921 --> 06:52.375
